item.title: Focus On You - Oprah Winfrey
item.description: Oprah Winfrey is a media mogul, actress, producer, and philanthropist. She is best known for her talk show, "The Oprah Winfrey Show," which ran from 1986 to 2011 and became one of the highest-rated talk show in television history. Its success helped her become the world’s first Black woman billionaire in 2003. Take action and strengthen your mind with The Resilient Mind Journal.
